item.title: Downtown West Palm Beach Food Tour
item.description: Bring your appetite, a bib, and a sense of culinary curiosity on this downtown West Palm Beach food tour. This five-stop foodie tour focuses on the locally-owned and award-winning restaurants that make up West Palm’s dining scene. Taste some of the most popular dishes at Kapow Noodle Bar and walk to the spot locals claim has the best Key Lime Pie in the city. You’ll also pop into the one of the oldest restaurants in town, Pistache French Bistro.

image.alt: Downtown West Palm Beach Food Tour

item.title: Guided Clear Kayak Eco-Tour of Jupiter
item.description: Discover the diverse wildlife of Jupiter with a clear kayak tour. Meet your guide for a small-group paddling adventure into mangroves and scenic waterways. Keep an eye out for a variety of wildlife such as manatees, dolphins, and colorful fish. See below the surface of the water through the clear, transparent kayak during the excursion.

image.alt: Guided Clear Kayak Eco-Tour of Jupiter

item.title: Scenic Sunset Cruise in West Palm Beach
item.description: Climb aboard a catamaran for a scenic sunset cruise departing from West Palm Beach. Admire views of the Palm Beaches and Peanut Island Park from the deck of a boat during this evening tour, including an on-board cash bar. Keep an eye out for wildlife including dolphins, manatees, and sea birds during this fun excursion on the water.

image.alt: Scenic Sunset Cruise in West Palm Beach

item.title: Half-Day Deep-Sea Fishing at Riviera Beach
item.description: Go deep-sea fishing at Riviera Beach with a half-day outing aboard a custom-built aluminum drift fishing boat. All equipment and a fishing license are provided, so you won’t need to do any extra planning. Just climb aboard, then enjoy cushioned seating on your way to nearby fishing grounds. With an experienced crew available throughout the trip, this outing is suited to everyone from beginners to experienced anglers.

image.alt: Half-Day Deep-Sea Fishing at Riviera Beach

item.title: 2 ½ - Hour Guided Snorkel Tour of Phil Foster Park, Free Videos!
item.description: Spend two fun-filled hours spotting stunning sea creatures with the help of an experienced and friendly local guide. Your tour leader has extensive knowledge of the marine preserve and shows you all the best spots for seeing a variety of Florida wildlife, from rays and starfish to octopi and moray eels. Unlike normal tours, explore hidden underwater treasures and learn about the ecosystem’s diverse marine life, behaviors, and anatomy.

image.alt: 2 ½ - Hour Guided Snorkel Tour of Phil Foster Park, Free Videos!

item.title: Beginner Scuba Diving Experience With Videos in West Palm Beach
item.description: We specialize in introducing beginners to the exciting world of scuba diving, so no prior experience or swimming skills are required to join our tour. Immerse yourself in the stunning waters of West Palm Beach, where you'll encounter vibrant fish, fascinating sea life, and even the occasional turtle. To make this adventure even more memorable, our instructors will capture short video clips of your experience and provide them to you at no extra cost, directly downloaded to your phone. Come explore the underwater beauty of West Palm Beach, Florida, with us!

image.alt: Beginner Scuba Diving Experience With Videos in West Palm Beach

item.title: Blue Heron Drift Fishing Family Friendly Charter
item.description: Spend some time out on the Florida waters and troll for fish during this family-friendly fishing excursion. Board your spacious vessel and head out to prime fishing grounds along with state-of-the-art navigation and fish-finding equipment. Then, cast your line for kingfish, snapper, grouper, mahi-mahi, barracuda, sailfish, and many other species.

image.alt: Blue Heron Drift Fishing Family Friendly Charter

item.title: Parasailing Palm Beach
item.description: Riviera Beach in Florida is absolutely stunning, but it can be really overcrowded especially on warm days. Beat the crowds on the beach by booking this Riviera Beach Parasailing Experience. You’ll go out on a boat and then parasail above the water to take in unobstructed views from the air.

image.alt: Parasailing Palm Beach

item.title: Historical Sightseeing Catamaran Cruise in Palm Beach
item.description: Discover the sights around Palm Beach as you embark on a historic sightseeing catamaran cruise. Climb aboard your vessel and sail around the Intercoastal Waterway to discover local beaches, Peanut Island Park, and the Henry Morrison Flagler Museum. While you sail, listen to narration about the history of the area.

image.alt: Historical Sightseeing Catamaran Cruise in Palm Beach

item.title: Bulk Candy Store Tour
item.description: Discover the history of candy, from ancient to modern times, during this tour in West Palm Beach. Visit the Bulk Candy Store and join a small group to learn how candy is made. Learn about the production process through the years, aided by live and video presentations, and enjoy samples of several candies.

image.alt: Bulk Candy Store Tour

item.title: Paddle Boarding Eco Adventure Tour Jupiter Florida - Singer Island
item.description: Paddle boarding through Florida can be one of the most beautiful but also one of the most daring things you do in the Sunshine State, especially if you don’t know the area well. Go with a naturalist guide and pass through the mangrove area, Singer Island, and the Jupiter waterways as you look for wildlife and learn about the unique ecosystem of the region.

image.alt: Paddle Boarding Eco Adventure Tour Jupiter Florida - Singer Island

item.title: Wild & Scenic Loxahatchee River Guided Tour
item.description: The Loxahatchee River is a National Wild and Scenic River in Florida, but the stretch is more than seven miles (11 kilometers) long, and if you don’t know which way to go, it could get confusing. This Loxahatchee River Kayak Tour lets you cruise the river with a guide and a group in a kayak. Keep an eye out for animals hidden in the beautiful Cypress tree forest along the route.

image.alt: Wild & Scenic Loxahatchee River Guided Tour

item.title: Food Tour of Historic West Palm Beach Neighborhoods
item.description: Discover culinary gems of the West Palm Beach neighborhood on this tasting tour. Explore this trendy neighborhood by van and visit the Grandview Public Market, meet award-winning chefs, stop for tacos prepared by a Food Network champion, sample Cuban cuisine, and more. Dine in unique locations along the way and enjoy commentary from your guide on the West Palm culinary scene.

image.alt: Food Tour of Historic West Palm Beach Neighborhoods

item.title: Guided Snorkel Experience, Free Videos in West Palm Beach
item.description: Explore the underwater world without having to worry during this guided snorkeling experience in West Palm Beach. Great for beginners and non-swimmers, dive into a realm of vibrant fish, captivating sea creatures, and the occasional visit from turtles. Dedicated instructors will even film your adventure as a complimentary service, delivering the magic straight to your phone. Immerse yourself in convenience, expertise, and ocean marvels.

image.alt: Guided Snorkel Experience, Free Videos in West Palm Beach

item.title: Guided Jet Snorkel Experience, Free Videos in West Palm Beach
item.description: Zoom through the waters of West Palm beach holding a jet snorkel on this private tour just for you and your group. Your instructor gives thorough instructions, so beginners are welcome. After learning the fundamentals, then head into the water to see what kinds of fish live off the shores of West Palm Beach.

image.alt: Guided Jet Snorkel Experience, Free Videos in West Palm Beach

item.title: Clear Kayak Eco Tour in Jupiter, Florida
item.description: Join us for a clear kayaking tour along the waterways of Jupiter, Florida! Our guides provide in-depth information about the plants, animals, and unique features of the area. While paddling through the clear waters, we'll keep an eye out for a variety of marine creatures like manatees, rays, sea turtles, and a multitude of vibrant fish. Additionally, we'll have opportunities to observe a diverse array of birds, such as pelicans, herons, owls, and ospreys. This eco-friendly and conservation-focused activity in Jupiter offers a rare opportunity to connect with nature and create lasting memories.

image.alt: Clear Kayak Eco Tour in Jupiter, Florida

item.title: Prohibition Dinner & Drinks Tour
item.description: From street art murals to wine gardens, see a variety of spots in West Palm Beach you may have missed if you went exploring solo. This Walking Happy Hour Tour in Downtown West Palm Beach takes you to trendy and low-key spots where you can sample fun drinks and tasty bites, while getting acquainted with the area. Plus, your guide brushes on the city’s prohibition past for a bit of history, too.

image.alt: Prohibition Dinner & Drinks Tour

item.title: Jupiter Island Sunset Cruise
item.description: With a small population of less than 900 people, Jupiter Island must be reached by boat. Avoid the hassle of renting your own and take this Jupiter Island Sunset Cruise to become more familiar with the area. See spots such as Jupiter Inlet Lighthouse, Dubois Park, and Johnathan Dickerson State Park while your captain tells you about the history along the way. Plus, you’ll be sailing at sunset—the most beautiful time of day.

image.alt: Jupiter Island Sunset Cruise

item.title: Mornings in the Market Food Tour
item.description: Start your day with some delicious food and learn about the area’s history with the help of a resident guide. You’ll eat like a local, skip the lines, and chat with vendors who live and breathe Floridian food. There’s plenty to learn about the area’s agriculture, too. Just make sure you bring your appetite.

image.alt: Mornings in the Market Food Tour

item.title: Parasailing Adventure in West Palm Beach
item.description: Make memories that will last a lifetime on this 1.5-hour parasailing excursion. Whether you think it’s peaceful or you feel a rush of adrenalin as you begin to float into the sky, your captain will be on hand to make sure you stay safe and have fun. Be sure to keep your eyes peeled for dolphins, sea turtles, and other marine wildlife during the experience too.

image.alt: Parasailing Adventure in West Palm Beach

item.title: Flamingle Happy Hour Cruise
item.description: Looking for a perfectly relaxing & fun way to end your day or begin your evening? Join us on the only boat in Downtown West Palm Beach for a happy hour priced cruise along Palm Beach Island just before the sunset. Tropical drink specials, tropical music and beautiful scenery. 90 minute FUN boat ride for all ages aboard. Visit Palm Beach's 50' Catamaran, "Hakuna Matata" .

image.alt: Flamingle Happy Hour Cruise

item.title: Palm Beach Island Sunset Cruise
item.description:
Enjoy the amazing views of Palm Beach during sunset from the intracoastal waterway. Learn about the history of the area and see the beautiful homes of the rich and famous. You just might see a view mega yachts.
Our catamaran cruisers are fully equipped with all the necessities to ensure our guests have a safe, fun, and memorable trip. Both of our boats have a nice open concept, allowing you to move freely around the boat while underway. There is a bar stocked full with and array of wine, beer, and soda so you can enjoy a nice cold beverage while admiring the beautiful views. Ample cushioned seating, along with a bathroom is on board.

image.alt: Palm Beach Island Sunset Cruise

item.title: Clear Kayak Peanut Island Guided Tour Palm Beach Singer Island
item.description:
Take a tour to Peanut Island with a Florida native guide as you float above sea life, sandbars & shipwrecks in a clear kayak that allows you to see the underwater world. Explore historic Peanut Island with chances to encounter wildlife such as Fish, manatee, turtles, starfish, Iguana and stingray.
WEIGHT LIMIT 250 POUNDS per 1 person & 425 combined weight tandem. All even number bookings will be paired tandem. We recommend proper swimwear or activewear, water shoes, and sunscreen! Ages 5+ Ages 17 & under must be accompanied by an adult. All bookings with 1+ person will be Paired Tandem. (Not wheelchair accessible)

image.alt: Clear Kayak Peanut Island Guided Tour Palm Beach Singer Island

item.title: NIGHT TIME Guided Snorkel tour of Phil Foster park
item.description:
On this private guided tour of the #1 Snorkel site in North America, experience nocturnal creatures beyond your imagination in an environment completely devoid of light. With our local professional guide you'll swim through a habitat of grassy/sandy ocean bottom with scattered coral reefs using a powerful underwater flashlight to search out unseen marine wildlife. Just a short distance from the shoreline is where you'll be exploring this incredibly unique and diverse ecosystem.
This tour is designed to be small and intimate to create a special and unique once in a life time experience.
This tour is truly all inclusive as we provide all snorkel equipment, wetsuits, flashlight, floatation devices and post snorkel snacks/drinks to enjoy after a satisfying swim in the night time sea. Fresh water showers to rinse off, and towels to dry and warm yourself, will also be provided.
If you’re scared of the dark, this tour is NOT for you! Come for a swim and leave with unforgettable memories!!

image.alt: NIGHT TIME Guided Snorkel tour of Phil Foster park
